name: Brazilian Body Wave
description:
The Dionne Hair Collection brings you the very best quality hair available in the marketplace. The Dionne Hair Collection guarantees that the hair you purchase will be of the highest quality without harmful processing and chemicals.  Hair from The Dionne Hair Collection is guaranteed to be 100% VIRGIN hair and will not tangle, will last longer, and look more natural than other hair being offered. All of our bundles are full and ultra beautiful.

The Dionne Collection brings you our Brazilian body Wave hair extension. Our Brazilian body wave hair holds its wave pattern after straightening and washing. Our Hair can be dyed into any color that you want.

Each bundle of our flawless hair extensions are:

3.5 -4 ounces (12 ounces is needed for a full sew-in)
100% Virgin Human Hair
Reusable
Single Drawn Hair
Grade A Quality
Tangle-Free
Full Cuticle
Minimal to No Shedding
Micro-Machine Wefted

Note: In order to provide individual attention and care of your order, please allow 2-7 business days for shipping. Please note that your hair may APPEAR shorter than the stated length, particularly our Brazilian body wave and ocean wave. All hair is measured as STRAIGHTENED.
